# Target/victim datasets and trained model artifacts — EXTERNAL INPUTS, never source.
# The Kaggle credit-card dataset is the TARGET being evaluated, not Crucible code.
# We commit the fetch+train scripts and a checksum manifest, never the bytes.
# Path is relocatable via CRUCIBLE_DATA_DIR (defaults to ./data).
/data/
/artifacts/
*.lgb
*.csv
*.csv.gz
*.parquet
